{"tid":1810151,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港旅遊發展局 : 滙豐總行大廈","createTime":"2020-01-03T15:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T15:26:23.000Z","uid":304432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b3495fbb56d9fe75bc355002f4cbcfd0caf593c5","tid":1810151,"uid":304432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T15:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.discoverhongkong.com/tc/images/see-do/culture-heritage/contents/HSBC_lion_chinese.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.discoverhongkong.com%2Ftc%2Fimages%2Fsee-do%2Fculture-heritage%2Fcontents%2FHSBC_lion_chinese.jpg&h=ceb21eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n史提芬（Stephen）及施迪（Stitt），是滙豐總行大廈外的兩隻銅獅子，自1935年起守衛滙豐銀行的大門，一直見證著銀行的光輝歲月。史提芬及施迪歷盡滄桑，曾經在二戰期間，遭日軍運返日本以圖回爐取銅，後來日軍戰敗，美軍遂將它們運返香港。現在，您還可以在史提芬的身上，看到戰時留下的子彈「傷痕」。<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n好紅喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}